room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped" by Escape Dalton in Dalton
room_description: You have been kidnapped but managed to escape from your captor. You are on foot, and see in the distance an old country store and dilapidated home. This is your only chance at survival. You must break in, find the keys to the old vehicle parked out back, and escape before your captor catches you! But you must hurry, he is hot on your trail and will catch up to you in only one hour!
